steps.name: I enter a "London" in the search text box
I select "£250,000" from Min price dropdown
I select "£400,000" from Max price dropdown
I select "Farms/land" from Property type dropdown
I select "No min" from Bedrooms dropdown
a list of "Property" in "London" are displayed
